1 Data Management

f20_1051data <- readdata('f20_1051data')
f20_diskdata <- readdata('f20_diskdata')
f20_eqdata <- readdata('f20_eqdata')
f40_1051data <- readdata('f40_1051data')
f40_diskdata <- readdata('f40_diskdata')
f40_eqdata <- readdata('f40_eqdata')
f60_1051data <- readdata('f60_1051data')
f60_diskdata <- readdata('f60_diskdata')
f60_eqdata <- readdata('f60_eqdata')

Each of the CSV files generated from the HDF5 Parser contains a dataset for a particular property. Each one is read into a data frame, and the returned data set is a list of all the data frames, appropriately named. The dataset specifically for CCA is read slightly differently because the headers already exist.

2 Property Visualizations

plotStressStrain <- function(dataset, maxSteps = 10){
  for (step in 1:maxSteps){
    print(ggplot() + 
        geom_point(aes(x = dataset$GrainMeanEVM[[step]], y = dataset$GrainMeanSVM[[step]])) +
        xlim(0, 0.06) +
        ylim(0, 1200) + 
        ggtitle(paste('Stress Strain Curve - ', deparse(substitute(dataset)) ,' Step ', step, sep='')) +
        xlab('Grain Mean EVM') +
        ylab('Grain Mean SVM'))
  }
}

plotSVMDistr <- function(dataset, maxSteps = 10, ylimit = 0.03, Grain1 = F, bin = 50){
  name = deparse(substitute(dataset))
  if (Grain1 == F) {
    dataset$GrainMinSVM = dataset$GrainMinSVM[-1,]
    dataset$GrainMedianSVM = dataset$GrainMedianSVM[-1,]
    dataset$GrainMaxSVM = dataset$GrainMaxSVM[-1,]
  }
  for (step in 1:maxSteps){
    print(ggplot() +
            geom_density(aes(x = dataset$GrainMinSVM[[step]], color = 'Min')) +
            geom_histogram(alpha = 0.2, aes(x = dataset$GrainMinSVM[[step]], y = ..density.., color = 'Min'), bins = bin) +
            geom_density(aes(x = dataset$GrainMedianSVM[[step]], color = 'Median')) +
            geom_histogram(alpha = 0.2, aes(x = dataset$GrainMedianSVM[[step]], y = ..density.., color = 'Median'), bins = bin) +
            geom_density(aes(x = dataset$GrainMaxSVM[[step]], color = 'Max')) +
            geom_histogram(alpha = 0.2, aes(x = dataset$GrainMaxSVM[[step]], y = ..density.., color = 'Max'), bins = bin) +
            xlim(0, signif(max(dataset$GrainMaxSVM), 2) + 100) + 
            ylim(0, ylimit) + 
            ggtitle(paste('SVM Distribution - ', name, ' Step ', step, sep='')) +
            xlab('Grain SVM (MPa)') + 
            ylab('Density') + 
            guides(color = guide_legend(title = 'Property'))
            )
  }
}

plotEVMDistr <- function(dataset, maxSteps = 10, Grain1 = F, bin = 50) {
  name = deparse(substitute(dataset))
  if (Grain1 == F){
    dataset$GrainMinEVM = dataset$GrainMinEVM[-1,]
    dataset$GrainMedianEVM = dataset$GrainMedianEVM[-1, ]
    dataset$GrainMaxEVM = dataset$GrainMaxEVM[-1,]
  }
  for (step in 1:maxSteps) {
    print(ggplot() + 
            geom_density(aes(x = dataset$GrainMinEVM[[step]], color = 'Min')) +
            geom_histogram(alpha = 0.2, aes(x = dataset$GrainMinEVM[[step]], y = ..density.., color = 'Min'), bins = bin) + 
            geom_density(aes(x = dataset$GrainMedianEVM[[step]], color = 'Median')) +
            geom_histogram(alpha = 0.2, aes(x = dataset$GrainMedianEVM[[step]],y= ..density.., color='Median'), bins=bin) +
            geom_density(aes(x = dataset$GrainMaxEVM[[step]], color = 'Max')) + 
            geom_histogram(alpha = 0.2, aes(x = dataset$GrainMaxEVM[[step]], y = ..density.., color = 'Max'), bins =bin) +
            xlim(0, signif(max(dataset$GrainMaxEVM), 1)) + 
            ggtitle(paste('EVM Distributions - ', name,' - Step ', step, sep='')) +
            xlab('Grain EVM') +
            ylab('Density') +
            guides(color = guide_legend(title = 'Property'))
          )
  }
}


plotSlipSystems <- function(dataset, maxSteps = 10) {
  for (step in 1:maxSteps){
    print(ggplot() + 
            geom_histogram(aes(x = dataset$SlipSystems[[step]], y=..count..), bins = 40, alpha = 0.4) +
            xlim(0, 10) +
            ggtitle('Slip System Distribution')
    )
  }
}
